        {
            "id": 6010365,
            "title": "〈電子五哥營收〉英業達受匯率影響5月營收微幅月減 持續看好AI伺服器成長動能",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>英業達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2356:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2356\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2356-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日公告 5 月營收 612.03 億元，受到匯率波動影響，微幅月減，不過年增逾 1 成，仍創歷年同期新高。英業達指出，持續看好下半年 AI 伺服器的成長動能，並指出下半年出貨主力將轉為 L6 系列產品。 </p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6010365%2Fl%2Ff2634d25534ed2d11f422e4b42b6546c.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">英業達受匯率影響5月營收微幅月減，持續看好AI伺服器成長動能。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>英業達 5 月營收 612.03 億元，月減 1.44%，年增 17.29%；累計今年前 5 月營收 2803.37 億元，年增 19.94%。 </p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>至於筆電出貨，5 月出貨 180 萬台，季對季、年對年皆成長 5.88%。英業達指出，6 月將有季底拉貨效應，預期季對季將有中個位數百分比的成長，不過受到關稅政策影響，客戶提前拉貨，預期上半年與下半年將持平，全年則是成長低個位數百分比。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>伺服器方面，英業達則指出，整體伺服器產品季對季將有雙位數成長，全年則是中至高個位數百分比的成長。其中，AI 伺服器成長動能仍然強勁，預期季對季有雙位數百分比的成長，下半年也將持續成長。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>不過英業達提到，上半年出貨機型主要為 Hopper 系列產品，單價 (ASP) 較高，下半年出貨主力則轉為 L6 系列產品，包含 B200、B300，對於營收貢獻相對較低。產品組合改變，加上匯率因素影響，預期整體營收上下半年將持平。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>另外，英業達也提到，已取得中東伺服器訂單，主要透過既有客戶及系統廠出貨，不過這方面目前貢獻仍不高，主因為客戶產品多為 B300，預期 B300 在今年第四季或明年初放量後，將進一步挹注。 </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
